<div class="related-campaign__text">
<div class="related-campaign__title">
<span class="f5 f4-ns lh-title serif">Coronavirus - protecting workers</span>
</div>
<div class="related-campaign__description">
<span class="f6 lh-copy sans-serif">The coronavirus pandemic poses huge risks to workers’ health, jobs and livelihoods. Unions stand ready to work with government to do everything we can to protect health, jobs, and livelihoods.</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</a>
</div>
<div class="related-campaign">
