<div class="related-campaign__text">
<div class="related-campaign__title">
<span class="f5 f4-ns lh-title serif">We need decent pay and secure work for key workers</span>
</div>
<div class="related-campaign__description">
<span class="f6 lh-copy sans-serif">TUC campaign: We need the government to raise the minimum wage, give public sector workers a real payrise, and ban the zero hours contracts that keep workers poor. </span>
</div>
